	&lt;p&gt;One of the recurring annoyances when designing websites is ensuring alignment of elements on a web page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Most design applications have the provision of an overlay grid. With very little effort we can add a simple grid to any web page and use it to ensure alignment of elements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&#34;more-527&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
